measurements.description: Approximately one hundred fifty-six flowers and 18 buds on 37 3-cm inflorescences; plant 35cm wide, 25cm high, 96cm circumference, mounted in 13-cm square plastic basket; sepals and petals white; lip white, midlobe overlaid lavendar two-thirds basally, side lobes overlaid pale green; column green; substance firm; texture matte.
